  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This clinical trial is going to compare the single-port and multi-port laparoscopic colectomy
      for colon cancer treatment, in terms of safety, efficacy, and cost.

      The investigators hypothesize that the single-port laparoscopic colectomy is not inferior to
      multiport laparoscopic colectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This clinical trial is a multicenter prospective randomized trial to compare the single-port
      and multi-port laparoscopic colectomy for colon cancer treatment.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
